name: cineMaErosPG_V4
description:
This is a merge of the following models:

  • maErosMix: + Art & Eros (aEros) - A tribute to beauty

  • maErosMix: + Mars Mix v0.1

  • maErosPG_V4: + RPG V4

  • cineMaErosPG_V4: + Cine Diffusion V3

  • cineMaErosPG_V4_UF: Fixed Clip and UNet with 0.001% of SD1.5

  • Baked in VAE: vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned.safetensors

I mainly use it for photoreal women: pictures, portraits, candids, fashion shows, softcore, erotic nudes...
I don't really know how it would deal with hardcore prompts, or different styles. I'd be curious to see whatever you can make much different than my examples.

My typical workflow, although I'd recommend to experiment a lot with your own settings until you find your style:

  • Sampling method: Heun (sometimes DPM++ SDE Karras)

  • Sampling steps: 50

  • Width: 512

  • Height: 768

  • CFG Scale: 3~5

  • Hires. fix:

    • Upscaler: SwinIR_4x

    • Hires steps: 25

    • Denoising strength: 0.2~0.3

  • After Detailer (You will need this for full-body / wider shots):

    • ADetailer model: face_yolov8n.pt

    • Inpainting:

      • ADetailer CFG scale: 3~5 (usually I would set it 0.5 lower than the main CFG scale)

License: Dreamlike
